1. Download Jenkins.war
2. Open cmd and type in: "java -jar jenkins.war"
3. Open http://localhost:8080 in browser.
4. Run it everytime you want to work with jenkins.

CLI to run tests:
- Go to: "http://localhost:8080/cli/"
- Go to Jenkins folder and run via cmd:     java -jar jenkins-cli.jar -s http://localhost:8080/ -webSocket help
- Go to: "http://localhost:8080/cli/" and click "Build".
- Go to Jenkins folder and run via cmd:     java -jar jenkins-cli.jar -s http://localhost:8080/ -webSocket build JOB -s

Если проблема с аутентификацией то: java -jar jenkins-cli.jar -s http://localhost:8080/help --username ToPPi --password 123QWEasdZXC